426
00:49:40,160 --> 00:49:43,439
I'm trying to get them, and if we
don't get them by the end of the day

427
00:49:43,440 --> 00:49:45,620
we're going to be
deported back to Alaska,

428
00:49:45,621 --> 00:49:47,799
it'll take three months
