452
00:51:44,800 --> 00:51:48,760
to rescue the crew for the final leg
of the journey.

453
00:51:58,920 --> 00:52:01,879
Six days and 5,000 miles from home,

454
00:52:01,880 --> 00:52:04,280
the crew finally arrive
at the place that

455
00:52:04,281 --> 00:52:06,680
will be their home
for the next month.

456
00:52:13,480 --> 00:52:16,999
This is an active hunting camp
and, that evening, the team

